SB's (only spec slash) -&gt; advantage to attacking stealthers.<br>
<br>
This is the reason most SB's feel that the fights SB vs thrust/pierce assassin should be slanted toward the SB, because thrust/pierce trade their advantage to attacking SB's when they choose to spec thrust/pierce.  However, the SB vs Slash assassin should be 50-50. (I am not debating if this was actually working correctly in game, but in theory should be correct)<br>
